<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/639881-why-is-charles-murray-s-white-nationalist">Why is Charles Murray&#39;s white nationalist book so intriguing to some people? 

The man preaches Nazi-style eugenics for Pete&#39;s sake: Southern Poverty Law Center: &quot;Charles Murray has become one of the most influential social scientists in America, using racist pseudoscience and misleading statistics to argue that social inequality is caused by the genetic inferiority...&quot; https://www.splcenter.org/fighting-hate/extrem</a>
</div>
