        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer677630890" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer9448102445515306521">As others have pointed out, this book is racist nonsense, and a sterling example of white privilege. &apos;Hmmm, people of color are disproportionately poor and criminalized. Instead of accepting that our ancestors created, and that we perpetuate, a racist society that disenfranchises &quot;blacks&quot; and over-enfranchises &quot;whites&quot;, let&apos;s find a way to blame it all on the inherent inferiority of &quot;blacks&quot;.&apos; (Stephen J. Gould&apos;s Mismeasure Of A Man elegantly explains why the underlying science is without merit.</span>
  <span id="freeText9448102445515306521" style="display:none">As others have pointed out, this book is racist nonsense, and a sterling example of white privilege. 'Hmmm, people of color are disproportionately poor and criminalized. Instead of accepting that our ancestors created, and that we perpetuate, a racist society that disenfranchises "blacks" and over-enfranchises "whites", let's find a way to blame it all on the inherent inferiority of "blacks".' (Stephen J. Gould's Mismeasure Of A Man elegantly explains why the underlying science is without merit.)</span>
