<li class='cover' id='bookCover_12031563'>
<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/12031563-coming-apart"><img alt="Coming Apart: The State of White America, 1960-2010" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1333576558l/12031563._SX98_.jpg" />
